  "texts": [
    "The same topic-centered \"skills training\" modules can also be applied to the families as well: grief, depression, shame and guilt, anger and aggression, and so on.",
    "In the same way, programs for the prevention of suicides, control and management of the use of psychoactive substances and associated problems (for example, aggression) should be applied to families, as well as the available resources for their solution should be brought to their attention.",
    "Assistance to veterans at their place of residence is conducted in case of severe physical condition, or to provide crisis intervention, for example, in case of a threat of suicide or domestic violence.",
    "Various modules of crisis interventions and, if necessary, pharmacological intervention should be applied here.",
    "Working in a specialized hospital with veterans with complex cases of complex PTSD and PTSD with severe comorbid mental disorders."
  ]
}